description:
In this episode, we travel to the farm of Hiram Edson. It was here where a clearer and correct understanding of the sanctuary was developed after the prophecy and Great Disappointment of 1844. It is also the place where the two pillars of the Sabbath and the Sanctuary came together and is called the theological birthplace of Adventism.

To find out more information about Hiram Edson visit our website to read our extended article. 
https://lineagejourney.com/read/hiram-edson-the-theological-birthplace
